r previous work and constructing an average SED of high-energy emitting QSOs, i.e, type-2 QSOs and blazars. For public use, we also provide the EBL models obtained using different QSO SEDs at extreme-UV energies over a wide range of redshifts. These can be used to quantify uncertainties in the parameters derived from photoionization models and numerical simulations originating from the allowed variations in the UV background radiation.},
